The country's President Abdullah Gul said that it was unacceptable to impose complete bans on social media platforms such as Twitter.

'I hope this implementation won't last long,' he wrote. 

'One cannot approve of the complete closure of social media platforms,' Mr 
Gul tweeted.

He said only individual Internet pages should be blocked if
